We've moved to a new Instagram home and are excited to bring back our beloved flavors, starting with an irresistible offer: $1.90 Fresh Oysters! 🎉 Dive into this exquisite treat at our 14 Circular Road and 197 Jalan Besar locations.

Don't miss a beat of our culinary adventures:

Follow our new account 📲 https://www.instagram.com/vietspicesingapore/
Reserve your table via WhatsApp for a guaranteed spot 🍽️:
Circular Road WhatsApp Number : +65 9734 1761
Jalan Besar WhatsApp Number: +65 9427 6098
As a warm welcome, dine in and order any of our delectable food and drink items to indulge in our fresh, succulent oysters at this special price.

Rejoin our community for more tantalizing offers and updates. Let's make new memories together at Viet Spice! 🌊🥢 #NewBeginningsAtVietSpice #OysterPromotion #SGFoodies"
